			</div>
			<div class="col-md-5">
				<img src="images/featurette1.jpg" class="featurette-image img-responsive center-block" data-src="holder.js/300x200/auto" alt="Generic placeholder image">
			</div>
		</div>

		<hr class="featurette-divider">

		<div class="row featurette">
			<div class="col-md-7 col-md-push-5">
				<h2 class="featurette-heading">View our tasting notes and opinions here!</h2>
				<p class="lead">Picking out the right wine can be a daunting task, and we're happy to offer our tasting notes expert opinion. Visit the store location and our friendly staff will assist you.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-5 col-md-pull-7">
				<img src="images/featurette2.jpg" class="featurette-image img-responsive center-block" data-src="holder.js/300x200/auto" alt="Generic placeholder image">
			</div>
		</div>

		<hr class="featurette-divider">

		<div class="row featurette">
			<div class="col-md-7">
				<h2 class="featurette-heading">Mix things up with our cocktail recipes!</h2>
				<p class="lead">There's a drink for everyone, and finding it is a personal quest for many of our customers. Check out some of our "tried-and-true" recipes to help you get started!</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-5">
				<img src="images/featurette3.jpg" class="featurette-image img-responsive center-block" data-src="holder.js/300x200/auto" alt="Generic placeholder image">
			</div>
		</div>

		<hr class="featurette-divider">
